558
00:35:58,980 --> 00:36:01,290
They can raise the baby.

559
00:36:02,700 --> 00:36:05,179
She's a poor soul.

560
00:36:05,180 --> 00:36:07,280
All right, all right.

561
00:36:09,920 --> 00:36:12,949
We buried Mrs. Xu's body and after the Lantern Festival,

562
00:36:12,950 --> 00:36:14,772
I visited the Xu family.

563
00:36:14,774 --> 00:36:17,809
