568
00:36:29,700 --> 00:36:33,089
So I didn't tell anyone about her.

569
00:36:33,090 --> 00:36:36,389
After all, the baby did nothing wrong.

570
00:36:36,389 --> 00:36:38,799
So I brought her up as my own daughter.

571
00:36:38,799 --> 00:36:42,360
